{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"我在那高貴的夜間確已降示它"},{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你怎能知道那高貴的夜間是什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"那高貴的夜間, 勝過一千個月"},{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"眾天神和精神, 奉他們的主的命令, 為一切事務而在那夜間降臨"},{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"那夜間全是平安的, 直到黎明顯著的時侯。"}]}